UC6: retrive person belongs to city or state

mysql> select * from addressbook where city = 'nggpur' and state = 'maharashtra';
+------------+-----------+---------+--------+-------------+--------+--------------+------------------+
| first_name | last_name | address | city   | state       | zip    | phone_number | email            |
